00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.040
alam ko.

00:10:28.030 --> 00:10:28.870
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:10:31.790 --> 00:10:33.020
Kapag may nabubuhay,

00:10:33.020 --> 00:10:34.150
hindi mo sila pinahahalagahan.

00:10:35.150 --> 00:10:37.000
Kapag wala na sila, huwag magpeke ng pagmamahal.

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:39.320
Tingyan.

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:41.270
Maaari bang magkaroon ng halaga ang isang plorera sa isang buhay?

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:43.800
At bukod pa,

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.360
hindi man lang nagustuhan ng nanay ko ang vase na iyon.

00:10:47.240 --> 00:10:49.030
Iniisip mo lang na ginawa niya.

00:10:49.910 --> 00:10:52.180
Pinilit mo lahat ng ideya mo sa kanya.

00:10:53.180 --> 00:10:55.030
Wala na siya,
at hindi mo pa rin siya hahayaan.

00:10:59.030 --> 00:10:59.870
Buti nalang nasira.

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.390
Magaling yan.

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:11.390
Hindi mahalaga kung ikaw iyon.

00:11:11.870 --> 00:11:12.710
Nasaktan ka pa.

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:14.240
bibigyan kita ng credit.

00:11:15.150 --> 00:11:16.720
Panatilihin lang ang bar bilang side gig.

00:11:17.270 --> 00:11:18.750
Kapag gumaling ka na, halika hanapin mo ako.

00:11:19.270 --> 00:11:20.910
Manager ng Investment Department Ⅱ.

00:11:20.910 --> 00:11:21.750
Ang post ay sa iyo.

00:11:23.270 --> 00:11:24.130
Tiyo Zhou.

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:25.150
Nagbibiro ka siguro.

00:11:25.380 --> 00:11:26.320
Departamento ng Pamumuhunan Ⅱ.

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:28.000
Kailan pa ako nagbiro sayo?

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:30.000
Ang capital market
ay hindi tungkol sa seniority.

00:11:30.910 --> 00:11:31.910
Kung sasabihin kong kaya niya,

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.160
tapos siya.

00:11:33.790 --> 00:11:35.270
Hindi qualified si Zhou Lu, tama ba?

00:11:35.670 --> 00:11:36.630
Kwalipikado man o hindi,

00:11:36.630 --> 00:11:37.470
ako ang magdedesisyon.

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:42.920
Narito ang bagay.

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.200
Bakit ka kasali

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.240
lahat ng gulo lately?

00:11:47.910 --> 00:11:49.240
Lately bad mood ako.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.200
Mangyaring bigyan ako ng ilang espasyo.

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:54.480
O sa tingin mo ba ay masyadong malaya ang iyong asawa?

00:11:56.030 --> 00:11:57.600
Maaari ko siyang bigyan ng mas maraming trabaho kung gusto mo.

00:12:13.550 --> 00:12:15.600
Bakit mo dinala si Zhou Lu
sa negosyo?

00:12:17.320 --> 00:12:18.340
Huwag mo siyang maliitin.

00:12:27.030 --> 00:12:28.030
Nangyari ang ganyan.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.600
Bakit hindi mo ako tinawagan?

00:12:31.460 --> 00:12:32.320
ako…

00:12:32.330 --> 00:12:33.390
Kahapon ay si Meng Tang.

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:34.510
Ngayon ay si Zhou Lu.

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:36.910
Kaibigan mo si Meng Tang, naiintindihan ko.

00:12:37.550 --> 00:12:39.030
Ngunit si Zhou Lu ay iyong childhood pal

00:12:39.630 --> 00:12:40.550
at pati pamangkin ko.

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:42.320
May nangyari.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:43.870
Bakit hindi mo sinabi sa akin?

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:52.960
Well…

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:54.600
Sa totoo lang hindi ko alam

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:56.240
kung mahalaga sa iyo ang plorera na ito.

00:12:57.030 --> 00:12:59.870
Kung nakita mong nasira ito at nagalit,

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:01.790
mahihirapan sana siya.

00:13:02.550 --> 00:13:03.460
Bukod,

00:13:03.560 --> 00:13:05.100
Hindi ko binalak na itago ito sa iyo.

00:13:05.550 --> 00:13:06.870
sinadya ko

00:13:07.080 --> 00:13:08.960
linisin muna ang pangalan ni Zhou Lu,

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:10.240
tapos halika kausapin kita.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:12.910
Sina Meng Tang at Zhou Lu

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:14.720
importante ba talaga sayo?

00:13:15.690 --> 00:13:16.550
Mm-hm.

00:13:16.670 --> 00:13:17.600
Napakahalaga.

00:13:20.150 --> 00:13:21.320
Sino pa ang mahalaga sayo,

00:13:21.730 --> 00:13:22.600
bukod sa kanila?

00:13:22.720 --> 00:13:23.630
May buhay pa ba?

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:24.470
Oo.

00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:27.440
Tang.

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:28.680
Zhou Lu.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:30.800
Tita ko.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:31.840
Uh-huh.

00:13:32.270 --> 00:13:33.110
Mm-hm.

00:13:33.390 --> 00:13:34.230
yun lang?

00:13:35.090 --> 00:13:35.960
Oo, yun lang.

00:13:37.960 --> 00:13:39.290
Akala mo ba wala na ako for good?

00:13:42.030 --> 00:13:44.390
Hindi, buhay ka pa.

00:13:44.520 --> 00:13:45.470
Well, Jian Cheng,

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:47.000
Hindi ako nakapasok sa top 3.

00:13:47.590 --> 00:13:48.720
Atleast ilagay mo ako sa huli.

00:13:50.670 --> 00:13:52.360
So anong ginawa mo kaninang umaga?

00:13:54.150 --> 00:13:55.270
Sa ospital ngayong umaga.

00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:56.670
Nabugbog si Qin Zhuo

00:13:56.790 --> 00:13:57.630
ang ospital ni Tang.

00:13:58.390 --> 00:13:59.360
Okay lang ba si Tang?

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:01.040
Magaling si Meng Tang.

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:02.390
Si Qin Zhuo ang nasaktan.

00:14:04.870 --> 00:14:05.750
Nakakagaan ng loob.

